Packages 
Package Description
org.osframework.spring.chronicle
Classes supporting construction of Chronicle collections in a Spring BeanFactory.
org.osframework.spring.chronicle.map
Classes supporting construction of ChronicleMaps in a Spring BeanFactory.

Introduction

This document is the API specification for the Spring Framework - Chronicle Collection Support module. The API provides an extension of the Spring Framework to support declarative creation and injection of instances of the high-performance Chronicle collection data structures:

  • Chronicle Map
  • Chronicle Queue
  • Chronicle Set
